metadata.name: Bitcoin Angel Open Edition, Signed and Framed Limited Edition AR Print #1/1
metadata.description:
Winner of Auction Receives: 
- Physical framed signed print with AR implementation powered by Artivive. Signed Bitcoin Angel print is 31.5 inches by 23.6 inches (80 cm x 60 cm)
- Double matted bronze/copper finish custom wood frame and museum graded glass. Total frame measurements are 33.5 inches by 42 inches (85 cm by 107 cm)
- Bitcoin Angel # 3716/4158 will be airdrop
- Discounted access + exclusive add-ons to Castle Party 2023
- Scheduled virtual meet & greet with Trevor Jones and King of Midtown

** shipping costs of physical not included
